<p><strong>苗姑娘—肉丝泡椒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201106/abfd355a51e64737a406fd5f34494f42.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
