<p>04</p>
<p><strong>南山婆—西红柿酸汤粉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center" style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20201106/325db737d1634e5a923783e2d99f2626.png" max-width="600" /></p>
